reviews.text:
nice service nice food.

14000 min charge can enjoy private room with harbour sea view

ONLY COME HERE IF YOU WANT TO BE TREATED LIKE DIRT!

Average food. Extremely poor service.

An Impatient staff took our order. We ordered from the menu and the waitress said it's not enough for us, so we ordered 2 serves. Without looking or checking, she said there is only one serve left. She obviously didn't want to take our order.

Next table got the royal treatment. Our friend was told to move to make room even though the person behind her was seated far from their table.  This happened towards the end of the meal and our friend didn't move so it was the other person who had pushed back from table. 

I will never come back here.

Beautiful view of the harbour. And dim sum was brilliant

reviews.text: One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
When i asked the concierge where the washroom is , they said there is no washroom in the whole plaza... this is so weird

result.name: V-Point

reviews.text:
豫園 (銅鑼灣)
銅鑼灣登龍街18號 V Point 26樓

招牌松子鮮魚最開胃，可以加碗白飯送汁!

今天本來是去吃火鍋的，不過朋友病了轉了中餐。朋友本來電話去訂位說沒有位不能預訂，但之後我們walk in就有位。這家餐廳是全層分左面廳，右面廳。左面廳全部沒有景，右面廳裝修非常華麗。如果真的要去吃就要訂有景的一邊。

食物方面，我覚得整體ok, 我特別喜歡招牌松子魚，酸酸甜甜一整條，好味。脆皮素鴨也很出色。

如果想食高力豆沙或豆沙鍋餅就要預早叫定好樣廚房準備。那天我們大約10:30pm叫這兩款甜品，全都沒有！
One of the new high rise building consisting of upmarket restaurants.
餐飲為主，但宣傳唔多，下面又冇餐牌可以睇
貴價又難食的高檔菜式

I had only one drink there, so I can't say much about the food but the view is pretty good and the staff was super friendly. They even made some discount on the occasion of my b-day and offered some shots. I thinks its definitely worth trying, at least, once)
